    {
      "id": 53,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "4-Layer Audit Stack",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 22,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "| Layer | System | Retention | GDPR Controls |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **L1** | Temporal Workflow History | 30 days | Workflow IDs \u2014 no PII in workflow args |\n| **L2** | Phoenix OTel Spans | 90 days | PII filtered at OTel attribute level before export |\n| **L3** | structlog \u2192 Azure Monitor | 1 year | Logs anonymised; customer IDs hashed with SHA-256 |\n| **L4** | Database Decision Records | 5\u20137 years (AML regs) | Encrypted at rest; access via RBAC audit trail |\n\n> **Audit Report Generation**: Previously 2\u20133 days manual \u2192 now **< 2 minutes** automated via structured log queries  \n> *Update this panel manually when retention policies or architecture changes.*",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    },
