      "options": {
        "content": "| Level | Stage | Description | Status |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **L1** | Initial | Ad-hoc testing, no automation | \u2705 Complete |\n| **L2** | Developing | Basic CI gates, unit tests | \u2705 Complete |\n| **L3** | Defined | LLM-as-judge evals, Phoenix tracing | \u2705 **Current Level** |\n| **L4** | Managed | Full evaluator coverage, cost gates, SLA monitoring | \ud83d\udd04 In Progress |\n| **L5** | Optimizing | Continuous self-improvement, automated retraining gates | \ud83d\udcc5 Planned |\n\n> **Current AI Maturity Score**: Derived from CI gate pass rates + evaluator coverage  \n> *To make dynamic: derive maturity level from `(ci_gate_pass_rate > 0.9 AND evaluator_coverage > 0.8)` Prometheus rules*",
